Be inspired by our state-of-the-art studios, enjoy the authentic atmosphere of our beautiful campus, tip-toe through our library, get a feel for our lecture halls and experience our thoroughly equipped photography studio. This is an opportunity to meet our lecturers and gain first-hand experience on what visual communication, interactive development and film art are all about. For those of you interested in taking your drawing and design skills up a notch, go like our Open Window Facebook page and stand a chance to win a Wacom Intuous tablet. Follow the link for more! https://www.facebook.com/theopenwindow/videos/1465847680154948/ For more information, keep an eye on our Facebook event: https://www.facebook.com/events/290738781366670/.